title: Trending or Ending + TNF Preview, Bust-O-Rama - Fantasy Football Podcast for 9/29
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode headed into Week 4! On today’s fantasy football podcast, a look at player trends through three weeks. Will Myles Gaskin and Allen Robinson get on track? Will Cooper Kupp keep dominating? Plus, the Week 4 edition of Buy or Sell, and a Thursday Night Football preview of the Jaguars vs Bengals. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast -- Fantasy Football Podcast for September 29th, 2021.
  
 (03:50) - Buy or Sell
 (12:15) - NFL News 
 (17:35) - Trending or Ending
 (17:50) - Joe Burrow
 (21:05) - Myles Gaskin
 (28:00) - Allen Robinson
 (35:25) - Cooper Kupp / Robert Woods
 (42:15) - Thursday Night Preview: Jaguars vs Bengals
